    {
      "title": "[正面] The fact that this game has held my attention for...",
      "summary": "The fact that this game has held my attention for longer than three days with how busy my schedule is tells you good things about this game. \n\nI was baited by the Saya collaboration event and downloaded the game in an attempt to roll for her. Ultimately, I managed to get her, but I was hooked by the great story (at least for the first two chapters so far), the beautiful art, good music, and the overall Lovecraftian setting/atmosphere. I can't comment on how generous the gacha is, but I have not had much trouble getting the characters (i.e. the aforementioned Saya) that I wanted.\n\nI'm very much invested in the story at the moment and am putting in hours every day working on it so I don't see myself dropping this game anytime soon.",
      "source": "steam_review",
      "time": "2026-06-06T07:23:53+00:00",
      "url": "https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561198147749177/recommended/3052450",
