    {
      "title": "[正面] I was never a huge fan of card building gachas, mo...",
      "summary": "I was never a huge fan of card building gachas, mostly because it just felt like too much information thrown at me and I never had a chance to really understand what did what and why. But somehow this one game made me appreciate the genre.\n\nI definitely also love the art style and the story as well. While I'm not super far at the moment of typing this out, I've enjoyed what I have experienced! I also like that you can essentially skip the pvp part of the game, even if it's a different take on a common mode (characters do different things in the mode, etc).",
